The clocks sys_clk_pin and clk_out1_audio_pipe_hw_clk_wiz_0_0 are related (timed together) but they have no common primary clock. The design could fail in hardware. To find a timing path between these clocks, run the following command: report_timing -from [get_clocks sys_clk_pin] -to [get_clocks clk_out1_audio_pipe_hw_clk_wiz_0_0]
